{"tid":2419823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍親自指導 懲教海關逐步引入中式步操 消防警察稱暫無意取代英式步操","createTime":"2021-02-23T13:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T17:06:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd41760cfeac0cb7d9cda576bd0d9cbf7402fe9","tid":2419823,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qPzAwQRe4bAQ7vUEKNzgUpGUI5Y=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AD7YBWFNTZEB3AXNSDYRIETZ3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqPzAwQRe4bAQ7vUEKNzgUpGUI5Y%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAD7YBWFNTZEB3AXNSDYRIETZ3E.jpg&h=b4c0e6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xhcOJLmgNOtg6B4nUxhDMY2oGd8=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LUJTNHLYZRCOZKKKBLQAHCRV6U.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxhcOJLmgNOtg6B4nUxhDMY2oGd8%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLUJTNHLYZRCOZKKKBLQAHCRV6U.JPG&h=9609f982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有指解放軍駐港部隊由昨日（22日）起，派出10名駐港部隊三軍儀仗隊官兵到黄竹坑警察學院，向警隊、入境處等各大紀律部隊教授中式步操，為期兩星期，多名紀律部隊首長承認有派員到警察學院受訓，其中懲教署、海關稱會分階段引入中式步操。懲教署署長胡英明更稱希望學習中式步操，「我想㗎，我想㗎，因為我鍾意學新嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n各大紀律部隊首長今日被傳媒問到有否派員參與訓練，全部首長承認有派員參與，懲教署、海關稱會分階段引入中式步操；而警務處、消防處則指現階段未有轉用中式步操的計劃。本港五大紀律部隊現時仍沿用英式步操，日後會否全面轉用中式步操，各大紀律部隊首長均沒有明確回應。<br />\n<br />\n而《蘋果》記者今日再到黃竹坑警察學院直擊香港人員受訓情況，20多名香港紀律部隊人員身穿全套制服，以約10人一組一字排開，並聽從解放軍官指令立正。經解放軍官指導後，各香港人員各自嘗試中式步操，再按解放軍官指示進行中式步操。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署署長胡英明表示，懲教署有派員參與警察學院的中式步操訓練，並稱早前曾邀請解放軍教官教導懲教署人員有關中式步操。<br />\n<br />\n他指，將會分階段引入中式步操，強調已部署一段時間，儀仗隊將會加入中式步操。他稱相關做法也是跟隨入境處，視乎表演效果，才決定會否全面轉用中式步操。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否全面放棄英式步操，他指：「不排除呢個可能性。」被問到他會否學習中式步操，他則稱：「我想㗎，我想㗎，因為我鍾意學新嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/WPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FWPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv34lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=b78aa7dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210223%2FWPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ%2F&h=fc942f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210223/WPF3IH7HQZGRTBJ4C3OPFR52AQ/</a>"},{"pid":"4b9bd8be634793e693a8560c8f28c43dbd102997","tid":2419823,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:47:44.000Z","msg":"幾時學埋摺被"},{"pid":"6ba08220d8bb261b9c13adc9881c56736013ad5f","tid":2419823,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:48:54.000Z","msg":"唔做 gentlemen, 做土匪！折墮！"},{"pid":"f628919a6979c6373c5baad7e9928ff0e32d4a51","tid":2419823,"uid":344896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"他指，將會分階段引入中式步操，強調已部署一段時間，儀仗隊將會加入中式步操。<span class=\"red\">他稱相關做法也是跟隨入境處</span>，視乎表演效果，才決定會否全面轉用中式步操。<br />\n<br />\n想學咪直接講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3a3f926dcfb0c2c1b305057767ff5110919032","tid":2419823,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"我想㗎，我想㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751a515bff684f10687d744bbbf51bf523abf3f2","tid":2419823,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"想知坐監使唔使步操？"},{"pid":"d3076f77e0477c1cccf02e89c9e7eb49724ba3c5","tid":2419823,"uid":392446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"海關,入境前線好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d369e3675f2c02e0d4c5a3d045785654998fd3a2","tid":2419823,"uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"都好嘅，操返中式唔好影衰英國"},{"pid":"698a9a303d95588be018cdbc68ffdee65e3c9abb","tid":2419823,"uid":115096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"以後可能要改口<br />\n唔可以叫 &ldquo;Yes, Sir!&rdquo;<br />\n要叫 &ldquo;是，長官！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"26b200f4e5a3b24b8126aeca4e712761b17c30a8","tid":2419823,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f628919a6979c6373c5baad7e9928ff0e32d4a51","tid":2419823,"uid":344896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"他指，將會分階段引入中式步操，強調已部署一段時間，儀仗隊將會加入中式步操。<span class=\"red\">他稱相關做法也是跟隨入境處</span>，視乎表演效果，才決定會否全面轉用中式步操。<br />\n<br />\n想學咪直接講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T17:06:04.000Z","msg":"老移果套4不像wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}